title: David wise - Product review
description:
Watch O'Neill team rider and freeski half pipe Olympic gold medal winner David Wise, talk about what the Intel Jacket is all about. 

Product details:
In a choice of three colour blocks, this snow jacket combines three styles of fabric and packs a performance punch. For a special touch, David's life mantra, Embrace the opportunity, is embroidered on the inside.

- Shell: 100% Polyester
- Lining: 100% Polyester
- Filling: 100% Polyester
- Regular fit
